[*]Altogolik - support, ideas, source materials
[*]Stalker_Boss - Russian translation
[*]gwalls - English copyediting
[/list]

[size=4][b]Usage and License[/b][/size]
[list]
[*]Modpacks: allowed and encouraged. Keep the readme and license files.
[*]Addons, patches, integrations: allowed. Credit "AlifePlus by Damian Sirbu" visibly on your mod page.
[*]Reproducing the implementation in other software: not allowed, even with credit.
[*]Full license in LICENSE file and on GitHub.
[/list]

[size=4][b]Reporting issues and suggestions[/b][/size]
Open a bug report or a suggestion at [url=https://github.com/damiansirbu-stalker/AlifePlus/issues/new/choose]github.com/damiansirbu-stalker/AlifePlus/issues[/url]. Also discussed on the GAMMA, EFP, Anomaly, and Zona Discord servers.
Before posting, read this readme and the MCM options. Include exact steps to reproduce, xray.log and the mod debug log (MCM log level DEBUG), plus engine build, modlist, load order.
